data.title: 'Chunwan' 2023: Liveblog CMG Spring Festival Gala by What's on Weibo
data.meta_description: 'Chunwan' 2023: Liveblog CMG Spring Festival Gala by What's on Weibo As we bid the Year of the Tiger farewell, and welcome the Year of the Rabbit, it is time for the annual CMG Spring Festival. Watch the Gala together with What's on Weibo here and follow our liveblog to keep up with what's happening on screen and the latest on social media. - 24liveblog
data.text: As we bid the Year of the Tiger farewell, and welcome the Year of the Rabbit, it is time for the annual CMG Spring Festival. Watch the Gala together with What's on Weibo here and follow our liveblog to keep up with what's happening on screen and the latest on social media.
